metadata.name: The Spectrum Of Emotion
metadata.description:
Joy,  Sadness, Anger, Fear...  

What Do you See?

Rorschach's are Surrealist, Mirrored Abstract photo's that use tenants of the Psychological Ink Blot test as part of its foundation & are derived from various photos within my Photography portfolio. Each Photograph is designed to invoke subjective imagery based on the perception, imagination and psychological perspective of each individual holder. 

This Rorschach is an extension of the original Rorschach collection and exclusive to SuperRare.
